data.description: GREAT OPPORTUNITY!!!! Just Fall out of ESCROW WITH NO FAULT OF SELLER!! Welcome to your dream home!!!  Gorgeous Single story home located in a nice highly desirable neighborhood of North Fontana. As you step inside, you will be greeted by the new beautiful waterproof laminate flooring through out the living areas, and freshly painted interiors that immerse the entire house with a clean and inviting atmosphere throughout the property, New carpet in all the rooms. This charming property features 3 good size bedrooms + Office/Den which could possibly be used as 4th bedroom, 2 full bathrooms. The large Master bedroom with en suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. The spacious Kitchen and Family dining areas flows seamlessly together all to enhance both casual or more formal get-togethers, making this the perfect setting for entertaining large group. Fully custom landscaped front & backyard, A well functioning spa and shed in the backyard will stay, 2 Car attached garage and a convenient separate room for Washer/Dryer hook-ups. Parks are within walking distance, also conveniently located within close distance to all Shopping center, Schools , Restaurants. NO HOA!!! This property is a MUST SEE!! HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!!!GREAT VALUE!
